---
---

<section id="pricing" class="section section-tinted" aria-labelledby="pricing-heading">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">Packages</div>
      <h2 id="pricing-heading" class="section-h2">
        Simple website and care packages<br>
        <span class="text-amber">for small businesses, nationwide.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="section-subline">Start with a one-time website build, then keep the technical side managed with a monthly care plan. Professional business email can be added when your business needs it.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-phase-row reveal" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="pricing-phase pricing-phase-once">
        <span class="pricing-phase-num">01</span>
        <span class="pricing-phase-lbl">One-time website build</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-phase-arrow">→ then choose</div>
      <div class="pricing-phase pricing-phase-monthly">
        <span class="pricing-phase-num">02</span>
        <span class="pricing-phase-lbl">Monthly care plan</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-grid">

      <div class="pricing-card reveal" data-tier="website-build">
        <div class="tier-top">
          <div class="tier-label">Website Build</div>
          <h3 class="tier-name">Landing Page Website</h3>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="price-sign">$</span>
            <span class="price-num">1,000</span>
            <span class="price-per">upfront</span>
          </div>
          <p class="tier-line">For local businesses that need a clean, professional one-page website to explain their services and generate enquiries.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="tier-feats" role="list">
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Custom, mobile-friendly landing page</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Contact form with WhatsApp, phone and email buttons</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Basic SEO and Google Search Console setup</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Secure HTTPS, hosting and domain connection</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Launch support</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline btn-full">Start Website Build</a>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card pricing-featured reveal reveal-delay-1" data-tier="managed-care">
        <div class="featured-crown">Most Popular</div>
        <div class="tier-top">
          <div class="tier-label tier-label-amber">Monthly Care</div>
          <h3 class="tier-name">Managed Website Care</h3>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="price-sign">$</span>
            <span class="price-num">100</span>
            <span class="price-per">/mo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="tier-line">For businesses that want the website, hosting, domain, forms, SSL and basic SEO checks managed every month.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="tier-feats" role="list">
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Hosting, domain and SSL managed</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Contact form and enquiry link testing</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Basic SEO monitoring and Search Console checks</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Small monthly updates</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Basic security checks</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-amber btn-full">View Monthly Care</a>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card reveal reveal-delay-2" data-tier="care-plus">
        <div class="tier-top">
          <div class="tier-label">Care Plus</div>
          <h3 class="tier-name">Website Care Plus</h3>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="price-sign">$</span>
            <span class="price-num">150</span>
            <span class="price-per">/mo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="tier-line">For businesses that want extra monthly support, blog uploads or help managing website content updates.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="tier-feats" role="list">
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Everything in Managed Website Care</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Extra monthly support and priority replies</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> One blog upload per month, formatted</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> SEO titles and meta for blog posts</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Option to add professional business email</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline btn-full">Ask About Care Plus</a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- ── AI Agent package (premium feature band) ─────────── -->
    <div class="ai-pkg reveal" id="ai-agent">
      <div class="ai-pkg-grid" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="ai-pkg-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="ai-pkg-orb" aria-hidden="true"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
      <div class="ai-pkg-main">
        <div class="ai-pkg-tag"><span class="ai-pkg-dot"></span>New · AI</div>
        <h3 class="ai-pkg-name">AI Agent &amp; Reception</h3>
        <p class="ai-pkg-line">
          A 24/7 AI receptionist built into your website that answers customer questions
          instantly, captures leads, qualifies enquiries and books calls, all trained on
          your business.
        </p>
        <ul class="ai-pkg-feats" role="list">
          <li>Custom-trained on your services &amp; FAQs</li>
          <li>24/7 instant replies &amp; lead capture</li>
          <li>Books calls and routes enquiries</li>
          <li>Ongoing training, hosting &amp; monitoring</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="ai-pkg-side">
        <div class="ai-pkg-price">
          <span class="ai-from">from</span>
          <span class="ai-amt"><span class="ai-sign">$</span>1,500</span>
          <span class="ai-per">setup</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-pkg-sub">+ <strong>$149</strong> / month management</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-amber btn-full">Add an AI Agent</a>
        <a href="/packages" class="ai-pkg-link">See package details →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="addons-divider" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="addons-divider-line"></div>
      <span class="addons-divider-label">Add-ons &amp; Extras</span>
      <div class="addons-divider-line"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="offer-grid offer-grid-addons reveal reveal-delay-2" aria-label="ReadyStack Digital add-ons">
      <div class="offer-card">
        <div class="offer-kicker">Add-on</div>
        <h3 class="svc-name">Professional business email</h3>
        <p class="svc-desc">Add email such as info@yourdomain.com, with support for MX, SPF, DKIM and DMARC records.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="offer-card">
        <div class="offer-kicker">Add-on</div>
        <h3 class="svc-name">Monthly social media content</h3>
        <p class="svc-desc">Optional monthly content support for social posts, blog posts and branded content updates across Instagram, Facebook, TikTok and LinkedIn. <a href="/social">See social media support</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="offer-card">
        <div class="offer-kicker">Add-on</div>
        <h3 class="svc-name">Extra blog uploads</h3>
        <p class="svc-desc">Client-supplied blog posts can be uploaded, formatted and prepared with basic SEO settings.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="offer-card">
        <div class="offer-kicker">Quoted separately</div>
        <h3 class="svc-name">Extra pages or custom requests</h3>
        <p class="svc-desc">Additional pages, advanced SEO, content writing, logos and custom features are quoted based on scope.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-page-cta reveal">
      <a href="/packages" class="btn btn-amber btn-lg">Compare all packages</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg">Get a tailored quote</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pricing-page-cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  }

  /* Add-ons grid: balance four cards across the row */
  .offer-grid-addons {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }
  .offer-grid-addons .svc-desc a {
    color: var(--amber-600);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: var(--weight-medium);
  }
  .offer-grid-addons .svc-desc a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  @media (max-width: 1000px) {
    .offer-grid-addons { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .offer-grid-addons { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* ── AI Agent feature band ─────────────────────────────── */
  .ai-pkg {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    isolation: isolate;
    margin-top: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.28);
    background:
      radial-gradient(700px 300px at 85% 0%, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.16), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(600px 300px at 0% 100%, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.12), transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(150deg, #14171d, #0b0d10);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    color: #fff;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr minmax(260px, 320px);
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    padding: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .ai-pkg-grid {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0; pointer-events: none;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
    -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 30%, black, transparent 75%);
    mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 30%, black, transparent 75%);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .ai-pkg-glow {
    position: absolute; top: -40%; right: -10%; z-index: 0; pointer-events: none;
    width: 420px; height: 420px; max-width: 60%;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(245,158,11,0.22), transparent 65%);
    filter: blur(30px);
    animation: ai-pulse 5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes ai-pulse { 0%,100% { opacity: 0.7; } 50% { opacity: 1; } }
  .ai-pkg-orb {
    position: absolute; top: 18%; right: 8%; z-index: 0; width: 90px; height: 90px;
    pointer-events: none; opacity: 0.8;
  }
  .ai-pkg-orb span {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; border-radius: 50%; border: 1.5px solid transparent;
  }
  .ai-pkg-orb span:nth-child(1) { border-top-color: rgba(245,158,11,0.8); animation: ai-spin 4s linear infinite; }
  .ai-pkg-orb span:nth-child(2) { inset: 12px; border-bottom-color: rgba(16,185,129,0.7); animation: ai-spin 6s linear infinite reverse; }
  .ai-pkg-orb span:nth-child(3) { inset: 24px; border-left-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); animation: ai-spin 8s linear infinite; }
  @keyframes ai-spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

  .ai-pkg-main, .ai-pkg-side { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .ai-pkg-tag {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.45rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #FCD34D;
    background: rgba(245,158,11,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.35);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem; border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }
  .ai-pkg-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--green); box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--green); }
  .ai-pkg-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 1.1rem + 1.6vw, 2.2rem); letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: #fff; margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
  }
  .ai-pkg-line { font-size: var(--text-md); line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); max-width: 56ch; margin-bottom: 1.1rem; }
  .ai-pkg-feats { list-style: none; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.5rem 1rem; }
  .ai-pkg-feats li {
    position: relative; padding-left: 1.5rem; font-size: var(--text-sm); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
  }
  .ai-pkg-feats li::before {
    content: ""; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0.4em; width: 9px; height: 9px;
    border-radius: 50%; background: var(--amber); box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(245,158,11,0.6);
  }
  .ai-pkg-side {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.75rem); text-align: center;
  }
  .ai-pkg-price { display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: center; gap: 0.3rem; }
  .ai-from { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
  .ai-amt { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: var(--weight-bold); font-size: 2.6rem; line-height: 1; color: #fff; letter-spacing: -0.03em; }
  .ai-sign { font-size: 1.4rem; vertical-align: super; }
  .ai-per { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
  .ai-pkg-sub { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin: 0.4rem 0 1.1rem; }
  .ai-pkg-sub strong { color: var(--amber-300); }
  .ai-pkg-link { display: inline-block; margin-top: 0.8rem; font-size: var(--text-sm); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); text-decoration: none; }
  .ai-pkg-link:hover { color: var(--amber-300); }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .ai-pkg { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ai-pkg-feats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ai-pkg-orb { display: none; }
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .ai-pkg-glow, .ai-pkg-orb span { animation: none !important; }
  }
</style>
